---
title: Zingy Grilled Chicken & Cucumber Salad with Garlic Butter Pumpkin Wedges
description: Fresh, zesty, and oh-so-satisfying! This lemon garlic chicken is tender, juicy, and bursting with flavour, perfectly paired with garlicky grilled pumpkin wedges. Add a refreshing cucumber salad for crunch, and you’ve got a wholesome, vibrant meal that’ll have everyone coming back food more. No BBQ? No worries! Just follow the oven method.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
